This is a version of the Unix command line wc tool.

Built using Node.js

Number of bytes in a file
option -C
CLI Test node ccwc -c test.txt

Number of lines in a file
option -l
CLI Test : node ccwc -l test.txt

Number of words in a file
option -W
CLI Test: node ccwc -w test.txt

Number of characters in a file or if the current locale doesnt support multibyte charcters this will match the -c option
option -M
CLI Test: node ccwc -m test.txt

Default Option no options provided
option -All options
CLI Test: node ccwc test.txt

Read from a standard input if no filename specified
CLI Test: cat text.txt | ccwc -l
